===Etymology 1===
Cognate with {{term|雨|same|rain}}. Found both alone and in compounds. Perhaps derived from /same/ > /ame/ with the lose of the initial /s/; see ''same''.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|[ame]|lang=ja}}

